Sentencas: This paper provides two types of control relevant models of planer solid oxide fuel cell system with different details.
Titulo: Control relevant modeling of planer solid oxide fuel cell system

Sentencas: Dynamic models of system components which include heat exchanger, reformer and after-burner are also provided along with the necessary formulation of a fuel cell connected in parallel with a capacitor.
Titulo: Control relevant modeling of planer solid oxide fuel cell system

Sentencas: Steady-state and dynamic simulations of fuel cell system for both types of models are performed.
Titulo: Control relevant modeling of planer solid oxide fuel cell system

Sentencas: The results indicate that both models are comparable in predicting stack voltage at lower current load.
Titulo: Control relevant modeling of planer solid oxide fuel cell system

Sentencas: But, the discrepancy in the stack voltage, power and temperature of different components become more prominent at higher current load.
Titulo: Control relevant modeling of planer solid oxide fuel cell system
